_sText:
This map was created for our New Year Event on the Jail-Break server.
It`s a real huge maze so you can try your luck and do your best to escape! 
It`s a great experience for those who will endure this course!

Other notes: 
❄ You can control the whole process via buttons behind the main house (check last screenshot).
❄ There is also a fake finish here on the map. Be careful! If you enter this one there will be a tangerine music xD
❄ After all 5 winners have passed the map other players have only 5 minutes to find the exit.

Credits: energetic $@@@time!

Happy New Year!!!
